column5: got to my spot and caught one carp almost instantly. but as the ducks get curious they want to come venture and see whats making the sound. had a mother and 2 babies follow me all morning. as the morning went caught 2 lost one.  the two baby ducks  small carp  bigger carp  mouth shot   for those going out today good luck it is windy.pfb
Always nice to have a little company while you're fishing isn't it???  Looks like it was a good day for you, nice pics.  Maureen
Nice report & pics of your carp,WTG!!!!!!   cheers
Nice job out there and great pics!  That last one though...ugh!! A face only a mother could love...LOL.
Oh Yeah - those lips don't need any botox.  Nice job.
Great report, though the last pic has to take the cake for disgusting pic of hte year!
